1. *Čuvar* je čuvao ulaz u zgradu. (The guard was guarding the entrance of the building.)
2. *Čuvar* je bio veoma budan. (The guard was very alert.)
3. *Čuvarima* je naređeno da prate putnike. (The guards were ordered to follow the passengers.)
4. *Čuvala* je svoju porodicu. (She was protecting her family.)
5. *Čuvan* je u zatvoru. (He is being kept in jail.)